Álvaro de Luna (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%81lvaro_de_Luna_(actor) 0 Álvaro de Luna Blanco (10 April 1935 – 2 November 2018) was a Spanish actor. He performed in more than one hundred films since 1961. He was most known for El Algarrobo in Curro Jiménez.In 1963 he appeared in El verdugo, by Luis García Berlanga. In 1987 he appeared in the TV series Vísperas.He died on 2 November 2018 from a hepatic insufficiency. Álvaro_de_Luna_Blanco ( 10_April_1935 – 2_November_2018 ) was a_Spanish_actor .
